Recipe.create(name: "Egyptian Eggs", ingredients: "1 slice Bread, 1 Egg, 1 tbsp Butter", directions: "Spread butter on each side of toast until completely covered. Take a regular sized cup, place in the center of the piece of bread and cut a circle into the bread. Take the circl from the bread and fry in pan on stove until brown. Once complete, take the pieve of bread(with center missing) and place in frying pan. Crack egg and place in the center of the piece of bread where bread is missing. Fry for 3 minutes, flip the bread and egg. Let sit in pan to fry for 2 more minutes and then serve.", meal_type: "Breakfast", user_id: 2)
